hesed, literally "an act of kindness" is the basis for morality for jewish sect
makes sense that a historically discriminated against group would develop a solidarity based religious morality
in that sense : religious kindness could be considered the wisdom of the most miserable and hated group in the eorld

hesed in that sense is understood as mutual aid in the pollitical sense and kindness in the personal sense.
a mark of morality that does not a transcendental heaven and reaard system to be valuable 
